<br />

<br />
-Remove ALL cooldowns (except for empire bribes that one makes sense)
<br />
-Remove "declare hostilities" sillyness - just blockade whoever whenever
<br />
-Fleets return instantly
<br />
-Fluffing is made harder (but not impossible) - dunno how but somehow...
<br />
-When a player die, all fleets die
<br />
-Salvage % when player loses a defensive battle
<br />
-Total council projects cost around 4B+
<br />
-Council donation limit removed
<br />
-Pmode is removed (except the initial 300 turn pmode)
<br />
-Mediation available only to "perfect subjects" and costs like 50-70 empire relation points
<br />
-Council that declares war cannot mediate out of it
<br />
-No tech/proj loss in death after first week (when RP costs decreases)
<br />
-lvl11 tech grants something that gives player CM bonus for x (like 300-500) turns in case of death
<br />
-new councils have new player admission disabled by default<br />_________________<br />&lt;blaze&gt; oh avrem me and smart decided youre the cruel mean hard part of nc
